<template>
<iframe allow="accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" data-src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/12EQpTwn4lY?autoplay=1" frameborder="0" loading="lazy" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/12EQpTwn4lY?autoplay=1" title="Kena: Scars of Kosmora - Announce Trailer | PS5 Games">
